            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the deep sea underwater target monitoring field and relates to a deep sea underwater target monitoring device and monitoring method. According to the deep sea underwater target monitoring device and monitoring method of the invention, alternating current capable of exciting seawater proton precession is generated in a transmitting coil, so that hydrogen protons in seawatercan transit to a high energy level; after a period of time, the emission current is turned off, the high-energy hydrogen protons gradually return to a low-energy state, and a large number of energy quanta with a Larmor frequency are released; magnetic resonance attenuation signals are induced in a receiving coil; and an underwater target is determined according to the features of received abnormal signals; the signal features of the monitoring device are obtained in real time through a data processing center established on the land; and after analysis and processing are performed, the parameters such as position, size, heading and speed of the underwater target are given. According to the deep sea underwater target monitoring device and monitoring method of the invention, the magnetic resonance technology is applied to deep sea underwater target monitoring, so that the deep sea underwater target monitoring device and monitoring method have the advantages of larger monitoring range, higher sensitivity, high accuracy of acquired information and the like compared with the prior art. With the deep sea underwater target monitoring device and monitoring method adopted, effective means of deep sea underwater target recognition and monitoring are expanded."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及深海水下目标监测领域，具体地来讲为种深海水下目标监测装置及监测方法，通过在发射线圈中产生能够激发海水氢核进动的交变电流，使海水中氢质子跃迁到高能级；段时间后关断发射电流，高能级氢质子逐渐回到低能级状态，释放出大量具有拉莫尔频率的能量子，在接收线圈中感应出磁共振衰减信号，根据接收到异常信号的特征完成对水下目标的确定。利用在陆地上建立的数据处理中心实时获得监测装置的信号特征，经过分析与处理后给出水下目标的位置、大小、航向、航速等特征。与现有技术相比，将磁共振技术应用于深海水下目标监测，具有监测范围更大、灵敏度更高、获得信息更准确等优势，进步拓展了深海水下目标识别与监测的有效途径。"
                }
            ]
